items.title: Survey finds 51% of college presidents alarmed by Trump's return
items.description: A little over half of college presidents responding to an annual survey fear that President Trump's second administration will hurt higher education.

items.title: Federal judge pauses Trump's federal worker buyout plan
items.description: A federal judge in Boston on Thursday temporarily halted the Trump administration's mass buyout plan for federal workers.

items.title: ICE hits limit on detention beds, releases migrants
items.description: Homeland Security's deportation agency has bumped up against its detention bed space limit and has begun to release illegal immigrants.
